                misty seas.Why does the sea-dog die?Halitosis is a dead sail.Lord, yer not blowing me
                without a strength!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style scoped lang="scss">
  .about {
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;

    &::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      opacity: 0.75;
      background-image: url("/portfolio/images/nav.webp");
      background-size: cover;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    &::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      opacity: 0.1;
      background-image: url("/portfolio/images/clouds.webp");
      background-size: cover;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .image {
      max-width: 80%;
      align-self: center;
      z-index: 9;
    }

    .text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 900px) {
    .about {
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }
  }
</style>